formfiller

Class EventSinks

  • java.lang.Object
    • formfiller.EventSinks

  • public class EventSinks
extends java.lang.Object
    The EventSinks class stores a collection of EventSink objects. EventSinks receives the presented ViewModel output from each use case and passes it to each EventSink in the collection.
